name: NATURAL ORGANIC MUSLIN 1/2 YARD
description:
Beautiful 100% Cotton Organic Muslin Fabric
This is for a fat quarter of high quality, 100% cotton organic muslin Fair Trade Cotton Certified by the Soil Association. Open weave muslin used for arts and crafts as well as packaging and straining teas and foods. This fabric is 1.3m when purchased by the half or full yard/metre. Please email if you require a specific size.

name: FRIDA'S GARDEN FRIDA KAHLO ALEXANDER HENRY FABRIC NATURAL PANEL
description:

FRIDA'S GARDEN (Natural Background) 
Features the very popular Frida Kahlo surrounded by Parrots,Monkeys,lush jungle plants on black background.
 Size: Approximately 22(w)x36 (l)inches or 92cm x 56cm 
2 Panels will be cut as a 1 yard 
4 Panels will be cut as a 2 yards 

Postage is $1.90 for 1 Panel within Australia. International postage $4.80 for 1 Panel (22x36 inches)
